column5: Things are getting worse than Canada Geese in a Mississauga park!
Lol, looks good Wayne! You staying in Ottawa tonight or going back to Marcs?  Happy Thanksgiving to you and your family, safe drive!

She's getting a ride from her BF's Aunt..so I can head North instead Bud! If I was going ...the truck may just not stop in Ottawa and I'd probably just throw her out at Bronson while doing about 110 on the 417 for Montreal! LOL  Hope you got your lips around a thigh or two yourself this weekend and went easy on the AD.

AD..... its something you have to ease into if you know what I mean....  Plenty of thigh, but only the tryptophan-free kind, I may have to go back to Montreal for a rest!!!.  Didja find someone to go north with ya?

Thats too funny wayne !!!!!! hey you could get real busy and stock-up for next years thanksgiving dinner..LOL..LOL..LOL.   man those wild turkeys are getting braver all the time,a few weeks ago i had to honk my horn to get them off the road,in front of my car????  cheers
Did you guys mind you were eating one of thiers? LOL
Wall, I'll be durned, right outside yer window, eh, Wayne!!
Chickens are just the same way.
So much for my theory of not getting a bird by sitting on the couch!!!

Grandmother said they killed them all off for a reason, they can do a lot of crop damage and they don't like bright colored mopars. My cousin painted an early 70's car and had it outside ready to pick up and a turkey pecked the ell out of it, didn't like the color, so don't trust them around the car.
